sequenceDiagram
    participant HW as setitimer
    participant SIG as SIGALRM Handler
    participant KB as kb_read_line()
    participant SD as sched_dispatch()
    participant TK as task_tick_all()

    HW->>SIG: fires every 50ms
    SIG->>SIG: tick_pending = 1
    Note over SIG: signal-safe only

    KB->>KB: read() blocked
    SIG-->>KB: EINTR interrupts read()
    KB->>SD: sched_dispatch()
    SD->>SD: tick_pending = 0
    SD->>TK: task_tick_all()
    TK->>TK: tick each READY task
    SD-->>KB: return
    KB->>KB: restart read()
